        *   The transformed character (codeword) is then written to the `encoderContext` using `encoderContext.writeCodeword()`.

3.  **`getEncodingMode()` Method:**
    *   Simply returns `5`, indicating this encoder handles Data Matrix Base256 encoding mode.

